      • getType

        public int getType(int row,
                   int col)
        Returns data type of the given column's value.

        Returned column types are

        • Cursor.FIELD_TYPE_INTEGER
        • Cursor.FIELD_TYPE_FLOAT
        • Cursor.FIELD_TYPE_STRING
        • Cursor.FIELD_TYPE_BLOB

        Parameters:
